# static modules
Style FvwmIdent* !Title, WindowListSkip, HandleWidth 2, Borderwidth 2, !Button 1, !Button 4, !Button 6
Style FvwmIconMan* !Title, !Handles, !Borders, Sticky, WindowListSkip, CirculateSkip, StaysOnBottom, NeverFocus
Style FvwmButtons* !Title, !Handles, BorderWidth 1, CirculateSkip, Sticky, WindowListSkip, StaysOnTop, NeverFocus
Style FvwmPager* !Title, HandleWidth 2, Borderwidth 2, Sticky, WindowListSkip, CirculateSkip, StaysOnBottom, NeverFocus


# Function: IconManClick
#
# This function is run from FvwmIconMan when the button is clicked.
DestroyFunc IconManClick
AddToFunc   IconManClick
+ I ThisWindow (Raised, !Shaded, !Iconic, CurrentPage) Iconify
+ I TestRc (Match) Break
+ I ThisWindow (!Raised) Raise
+ I ThisWindow (Shaded) WindowShade
+ I ThisWindow (Iconic) Iconify
+ I ThisWindow (AcceptsFocus) FlipFocus

# Function: ToggleTitle
#
# This function will toggle if fvwm shows the TitleBar.
DestroyFunc ToggleTitle
AddToFunc   ToggleTitle
+ I ThisWindow (State 1) WindowStyle Title
+ I TestRc (Match) State 1 False
+ I TestRc (Match) Break
+ I WindowStyle !Title
+ I State 1 True

DestroyModuleConfig FvwmIdent: *
*FvwmIdentBack #191970
*FvwmIdentFore #FFB600
*FvwmIdent: Font "xft:sans:pixelsize=10:antialias=true:hinting=slight"

